{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_10_01",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 1話 思い出のプレゼント",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（秋になると、麻奈のバースデーライブのことを思い出す）\n（遙子さんのおかげで会場は大盛り上がりだったっけ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（When autumn comes‚ I remember Mana’s birthday live.）\n（Thanks to Haruko-san‚ the venue was really lively.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.5999995548
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈も大いにはしゃいでいたが、少しだけ寂しそうに）\n（「琴乃にはフラれちゃった」と言っていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana was having fun too‚ but looked a little lonely）\n（and said‚ \"Kotono rejected me.\"）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4999995548,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4366.6669846,
          "startTime": 18.8666665394
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.2999995548
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.2999995548
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "こうやって、{user}さんと二人きりで\n歩くのも、なんだか久しぶりですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels like it's been a long time\nsince we walked like this‚ just the two of us‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "タクシーを好きなだけ使えればいいんだが\n時間に余裕があるなら経費削減ってことで……悪いな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wish we could use taxis as much as we want‚\nbut since we have time‚ let’s save on expenses… sorry about that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.5656008402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.7322666804
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ。{user}さんとゆっくり話せて\n私も嬉しいですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. I'm happy about having time\nto chat with you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "月ストがBIG4になってから、ずっとばたばたしてて\n最近はこういう時間もあまりなかったなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since Moon Tempest became BIG4‚ it’s been hectic‚\nand recently I haven’t had much time like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.8054184277
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "休みもなかなか取れなくて悪いな……。みんなと\nどこか遊びに行きたいなんて話にはならないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry we hardly get time off…hasn’t there been talk\nabout going out somewhere with everyone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4054192542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.8387517611
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "今はみんな、仕事が一番楽しいって感じですから\nあ。すずはこの間、遊園地に行きたいって叫んでました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right now‚ everyone feels like work is the most fun.\nOh‚ Suzu recently shouted that she wants to go to an amusement park.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "この前、星見市のテーマパークに行ってきたのになぁ\nまぁ涼しくなってきたし、外で遊ぶにはいい時期だよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We went to the Hoshimi City theme park just recently…\nWell‚ it’s getting cooler‚ so it’s a good time to play outside.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.9101132393,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.7434456189
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "遊園地と言えば……昔、お姉ちゃんと\n遊びに行ったことがあったっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of amusement parks… I remember\ngoing to one with my sister a long time ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.6808648746
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんがまだデビューする前……\n星見プロでレッスンを始めたばっかりの頃ですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was before my sister debuted…\nright after she started lessons at Hoshimi Pro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.833337911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それは初耳だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s news to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.8668054581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、お姉ちゃん言わなかったのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ didn’t she tell you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.2001387914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.0881219547
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんの誕生日のために、お小遣いを貯めて\n遊園地のチケットを買ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I saved my allowance for her birthday‚\nand bought amusement park tickets.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.033337911,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4266.66666669999,
          "startTime": 105.3000045777
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7399.999999999992,
          "startTime": 108.433337911
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_photo_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 104.5118858974
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてもお姉ちゃんに誕生日のサプライズをしたくて\n何も教えないで、当日、遊園地に連れてったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I really wanted to surprise my sister for her birthday.\nI didn’t tell her anything and took her to the park that day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.533337911,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6566.66208899999,
          "startTime": 116.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "遊園地の前についたところでチケットを出してみせて\n今日は私がお姉ちゃんをお祝いするから！　って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we got to the park entrance‚ I showed her the tickets\nand said‚ “Today I’m celebrating you!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.4666712444,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6629.8722460999925,
          "startTime": 125.0965434905
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-03.m4a",
          "delay": 7366.666746099994,
          "startTime": 125.8333379905
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "そうしたらお姉ちゃん、大勢の人がいる前で\n私を抱きしめて泣き出しちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then my sister hugged me and started crying\nin front of many people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.0000045777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それだけサプライズが嬉しかったってことだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That just shows how happy she was with the surprise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.0532063484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "それは分かるんですけど\nあの時は、さすがにちょっと恥ずかしかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew that‚\nbut at the time it was still a bit embarrassing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.2333348593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "メリーゴーランドに二人で一緒に乗ったんですけど\nお姉ちゃん、馬の上で私にぐりぐり頬ずりしてくるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We rode the merry-go-round together‚\nand she kept rubbing her cheek against mine on the horse.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.9333348593,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-03.m4a",
          "delay": 3509.456571100003,
          "startTime": 143.9333348593
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "あんまりくっつかないでよって言っても\n今日くらいくっついてもいいじゃん？　って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even when I said‚ “Don’t stick so close‚”\nshe said‚ “It’s okay to stick close just for today‚ right?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.2666681927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "凄く想像出来るというか、目に浮かぶよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can totally imagine it‚ it’s easy to picture.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.2235372225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "喜んでくれてるのは、もちろん嬉しかったですけど\nいちいち大袈裟なんですよ、もう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I was happy she enjoyed it‚\nbut she was overly dramatic with everything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.600001526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
